replies.body:
Are you experiencing a black screen at the login screen (or where it should be) or is this happening after champ select or somewhere else? Most of the time, black screens in the client are caused by the client being unable to establish a solid link to the specific server you're trying to access. I'd recommend ensuring your local network settings are completely compatible with League by working through our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps caused any noticeable change.
